race.comment: LIKE A DIAMOND (3) disappointed last time as favourite but the form around her this campaign is sticking up everywhere you look. Peak fitness now, with Crowther's booking signalling intent. IN THE SUN (8) held on well to finish third last time out over this trip at Horsham after leading for much of the way. Will go forward and is expected to be in the finish again. FUGACITY (14) took advantage of the good draw and raced on the pace last start before tiring to finish sixth at Colac. Another bold showing is expected. MISS GATSBY (9) turned in a decent effort last start to finish second at Mt Gambier. This looks a good race for her and she is one of the key runners. MY TRUTH (2) returned with a bang at Moulamein and despite this being tougher, he can keep the ball rolling and make his presence felt.
